verbose_text: To reply at this double question, we analyzed the percentage of cell death induced by an TMZ+ Irrad treatment on primary cultured tumors cells obtained from the patient derived GBM samples (referred PCTC-GBMs) pre-treated or not by kinase inhibitors targeting the kinases implicated into the presence of high levels of pH3T6, pH3S10 or pH3Y41 in PCTC-GBM.
